{
  "stem": "2906.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They used to come and tell us that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Russia, they have everything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They have even matches, because the only thing there was matches.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they stayed in 1940, when they-- they start bombing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And people came running from the other side, from Hitler side.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they were telling, when Hitler comes, he-- he kills young boys.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1939, the-- the Russians came in with tanks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They split it up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This I remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- the people used to run out and see.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That they came with big tanks and things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And all night, the Polish people were shooting, because nothing they could do about it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They took away everything, And leave us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We all were lying in the floor, because, you know, we're afraid we'll get killed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The-- the-- the Communists took over, and they are the bosses.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Nothing you can do about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then in-- when they start bombing, 1940, they start bombing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I saw the bombs were coming straight at us, and they fall on the other side.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I still now-- not now, but in the beginning-- when I came out from the war, when it was thundering, I thought that the bombs are coming.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then the-- the people telling that they kill younger boys.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jewish people came from Hitler's side.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They run away.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were telling us that he kills young boys.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, my brother was a younger boy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He's in Israel now.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, this was the brother who was born in 1924.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Label ?] Aryeh.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my mother said, take your brother and go to the-- to the border from there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Russian border.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1941.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was not [? tolerant about ?] a lot of kids.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Younger kids, everybody was running away.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
